Install CLI (available from anywhere):
  mise run setup
  # or: uv tool install --force --editable .

Refresh / uninstall CLI:
  mise run install-cli
  mise run uninstall-cli

Dev:
  mise run install
  mise run test          # coverage gate ≥90%
  mise run test-fast

Help:
  redact help
  redact help patterns
  unredact -h
